@node 20260710_dev "20260710-dev"
@{b}20260710-dev@{ub}

@{i}Components in this release@{ui}:

  * @{fg shine}ptable.library 2.0-dev (10.07.2026)@{fg text} @{i}(new)@{ui}
  * @{fg shine}lsptres 1.0-dev (10.07.2026)@{fg text} @{i}(new)@{ui}

@{b}Partition Table library@{ub}

  * @{b}Unified partition scanning.@{ub} One scanner parses RDB, MBR, GPT, and flat
    (whole-disk FAT) partition tables and publishes every partition into a shared
    @{fg shine}partition.resource@{fg text} , now consumed by both @{fg shine}compactflash.device@{fg text} and @{fg shine}fat95@{fg text}
    instead of each carrying its own parser. See @{"  ptable.guide  " link "ptable.guide/Main"} .

@{b}Tools@{ub}

  * @{b}@{fg shine}lsptres@{fg text}@{ub}: a new CLI that lists the contents of @{fg shine}partition.resource@{fg text}. See @{"  lsptres.guide  " link "lsptres.guide/Main"}.

----------------------------------------
